.TH cando-monitor 1  "cando-monitor 0.1.0" 
.SH NAME
cando\-monitor \- Real\-time CAN bus monitoring utility for J1939 systems
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcando\-monitor\fR [\fB\-d\fR|\fB\-\-decoded\-only\fR] [\fB\-f\fR|\fB\-\-filter\fR] [\fB\-r\fR|\fB\-\-show\-raw\fR] [\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR] [\fB\-\-stats\-interval\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] <\fIINTERFACE\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Real\-time CAN bus monitoring utility for J1939 systems
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-d\fR, \fB\-\-decoded\-only\fR
Show only decoded messages (hide unknown messages)
.TP
\fB\-f\fR, \fB\-\-filter\fR \fI<FILTER>\fR
Show only specific message types (comma\-separated list)
.TP
\fB\-r\fR, \fB\-\-show\-raw\fR
Show raw hex dumps along with decoded messages
.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Quiet mode \- reduce output verbosity
.TP
\fB\-\-stats\-interval\fR \fI<STATS_INTERVAL>\fR [default: 30]
Show statistics every N seconds
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.TP
<\fIINTERFACE\fR>
CAN interface name (e.g., can0, vcan0)
.SH VERSION
v0.1.0
